Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: zxarray
Version: 0.10.2
Summary: Interface to 'zarr' similar to 'xarray'
Home-page: https://github.com/yrobink/zxarray
Author: Yoann Robin
Author-email: yoann.robin.k@gmail.com
